    {
      "text": "%md\n# Problem 1\n## How many \"properties\" are Bristol City Council (BCC) responsible for (as owner, user or manager)?\n\nEach row is one property in this extract, so the row count answers the question within how the council defines a row in the file.",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "progress": 0,
      "config": {
        "tableHide": false,
        "editorSetting": {
