    {
      "text": "%md\n### Approach A: DataFrame API\n\nList distinct `Property Type` values, then count how many distinct values appear.",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "progress": 0,
      "config": {
        "tableHide": false,
        "editorSetting": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "editOnDblClick": true,
