    {
      "text": "%md\n# Problem 4\n## Histogram: total site area (hectares) by property type\n\nAggregate `Site Area (Hectares)` by `Property Type`, keep the top 15 by total area, then plot.",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "progress": 0,
      "config": {
